sub_title: Process Manager at McDermott International, Ltd
summary: A Process/Commissioning Manager with well over twenty years of extensive international engineering and construction industry experience related to refining and petrochemical projects. Experience includes Proposals, Process engineering studies, preparing basic engineering packages, FEEDs and full EPC execution, PMC services, Commissioning and Turn-over.
